### Step 1 : Deploy the Machine

Start by setting up the VPN connection.

Install OpenVPN:
sudo apt install openvpn

Download the VPN configuration file from TryHackMe access page.

Connect using OpenVPN:
sudo openvpn <file-name>.ovpn

Click Start Machine on THM and wait for the target IP to be assigned.

